Package: BalanceMate
Title: Mangaging, Pre-processing, And Processing Postural Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jean", "MonÃ©ger", , "moneger.jean@outlook.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1178-1896"))
Description: This package groups functions that facilitates postural data management (e.g., merging data files, time-stamping the files, creating epochs), pre-processing (e.g., applying filter), and processing (e.g., computing Center of Pressure, Sway Path Length). It is designed to work with .txt outputs exported from the AMTI software "NetForce".
